data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED!!! Seller offering 5k towards buyer closing costs --WATERFRONT PROPERTY-- direct deep water Gulf of Mexico access at any tide level. This is spectacular waterfront Hudson beach home located in the nautical community of SEA PINES is waiting for you. New roof 2022. Updates throughout the whole house including appliances, granite countertops and windows. Enjoy having enough square footage for multipurpose spaces. This 2 bedroom and 2 FULL bathroom home with a Florida room will not disappoint. The Florida room has access to the dining room and kitchen. Great golf cart and and boating community with restaurants and bars. Boat ramp about 100 feet away.
